snippet.title: Suzanne is Salty "That Crazy Feminist Writer"
snippet.description:
More than 4 years ago I moved to Costa Rica and it was nothing like described in any guidebook about retiring here. I'm trying to rectify that, covering what you really need to know to make your transition to another culture, and place go smoothly~ I sometimes rant here about YouTube drama, internet safety, the world of religion (I was a writer about Quiverfull theology for ten years over at Patheos at No Longer Quivering) and other frequent offenders like Jill Rodrigues and the New IFB. This is also the home of Handbaskets to Hell Book Reviews - doing reviews of books that are unbelievably terrible. This is the real me, accept no spoofs or substitutes. I sometimes talk about a life lived with the trials of MCAS. 

This is a commentary channel and these are merely my own personal opinions....allegedly! Please do not attack or harass anyone mentioned on the channel. We don't go real life because it's just tacky.
